document.topic_text: Home / Photos / Hyderabad / Andhra Pradesh Special Protection Force conducted mock drill Andhra Pradesh Special Protection Force conducted mock drill August 12, 2016 Hyderabad , Photos Leave a comment VIJAYAWADA, AUG 11 (UNI)- A team of Andhra Pradesh Special Protection Force (APSPF), conducting a mock drill of rescue operation a day ahead of 12-day Krishna River Pushkaram, in Vijayawada on Thursday.
